 "where \[DoubleStruckCapitalO] is the ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   SuperscriptBox["d", "2"], "\[Times]", 
   SuperscriptBox["d", "2"]}]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.536420399125372*^9, 3.536420416278985*^9}}],
 " zero matrix and \[DoubleStruckCapitalS] is a sparce ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  RowBox[{
   SuperscriptBox["d", "2"], "\[Times]", 
   SuperscriptBox["d", "2"]}]],
  CellChangeTimes->{{3.536420399125372*^9, 3.536420416278985*^9}}],
 " matrix with 3 (but occasionally only 2) 1s on each row and all other \
elements 0. Which means that about "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.5364200734872217`*^9, 3.5364202865811996`*^9}, {
  3.536420436736895*^9, 3.536420442250454*^9}}],

